	    </p>
	    <p>
	      <m>\sigma_1 = \sqrt{6}</m> and
	      <m>\sigma_2=\sqrt{5}</m>.  The right singular vectors
	      are the columns of <m>Q</m>.
	    </p>
	  </li>
	  <li>
	    <p>
	      <m>\uvec_1 = \twovec10</m> and
	      <m>\uvec_2=\twovec0{-1}</m>.
	    </p>
	  </li>
	  <li>
	    <p>
	      <me>
		U=\begin{bmatrix}
